%% Diagram: Optimistic Rollback
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: User action (assume success)
    Pending --> Confirmed: Server ACK + merge canonical
    Pending --> RolledBack: Server error or conflict
    Confirmed --> [*]
    RolledBack --> [*]: Restore prior snapshot + user message
